{"ja407:0.1":"Jataka ","ja407:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","ja407:0.3":"Gandharavagga ","ja407:0.4":"2. Mahakapijataka ","ja407:1.1":"“Attanam sankamam katva, ","ja407:1.2":"Yo sotthim samatarayi; ","ja407:1.3":"Kim tvam tesam kime tuyham, ","ja407:1.4":"Honti ete mahakapi”. ","ja407:2.1":"“Rajaham issaro tesam, ","ja407:2.2":"yuthassa pariharako; ","ja407:2.3":"Tesam sokaparetanam, ","ja407:2.4":"bhitanam te arindama. ","ja407:3.1":"Ullanghayitva attanam, ","ja407:3.2":"vissatthadhanuno satam; ","ja407:3.3":"Tato aparapadesu, ","ja407:3.4":"dalham bandham latagunam. ","ja407:4.1":"Chinnabbhamiva vatena, ","ja407:4.2":"Nunno rukkham upagamim; ","ja407:4.3":"Soham appabhavam tattha, ","ja407:4.4":"Sakham hatthehi aggahim. ","ja407:5.1":"Tam mam viyayatam santam, ","ja407:5.2":"sakhaya ca lataya ca; ","ja407:5.3":"Samanukkamanta padehi, ","ja407:5.4":"sotthim sakhamiga gata. ","ja407:6.1":"Tam mam na tapate bandho, ","ja407:6.2":"mato me na tapessati; ","ja407:6.3":"Sukhamaharitam tesam, ","ja407:6.4":"yesam rajjamakarayim. ","ja407:7.1":"Esa te upama raja, ","ja407:7.2":"tam sunohi arindama; ","ja407:7.3":"Ranna ratthassa yoggassa, ","ja407:7.4":"balassa nigamassa ca; ","ja407:7.5":"Sabbesam sukhametthabbam, ","ja407:7.6":"khattiyena pajanata”ti. ","ja407:8.1":"Mahakapijatakam dutiyam. "}